### ==== AUTH — ROPC Dev Flow (Development Only) ====
# WARNING: password flow is dev-only, never expose in production
# Requires AuthServer running at http://localhost:5001
# Requires admin@test.vn seeded in DB (password: Admin@Test123!)
# After success: copy access_token value to @token in _variables.http

### Get access token
POST {{authServerUrl}}/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=gsdt-dev-ropc&client_secret=dev-secret-not-for-production&username=admin@test.vn&password=Admin@Test123!&scope=openid profile email roles api

###

### Refresh token
# Paste your refresh_token from the login response below
POST {{authServerUrl}}/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=refresh_token&client_id=gsdt-dev-ropc&client_secret=dev-secret-not-for-production&refresh_token=PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
